Set Dataflow Notifications

You can receive an email notification when a dataflow job finishes, or when there are warnings or failures. You can also set a notification to be notified when a dataflow is still running after a specified length of time.

To set a dataflow notification:

* Edit CRM Analytics Dataflows
* Click the gear icon and then click Data Manager
* On the right of the dataflow, click  and select Notifications
* From the Notify Me About picklist, select what you want to be notified about
* To receive an elapsed time notification, select All Events from the Notify Me About options and specify the number of hours and minutes
title: Setting Up Dataflow Notifications in CRM Analytics
